 {"id":"franken_numpy-hsw8","title":"[PORT] Rust-port fnp-python raw constructors and text loaders","description":"Replace direct numpy passthroughs in crates/fnp-python/src/lib.rs for fromiter, fromstring, frombuffer, fromfile, loadtxt, and genfromtxt with Rust implementations derived from the current wrapper and parity-test spec. Success: these wrappers stop importing numpy at runtime, preserve current binary and text parsing semantics, and keep parity coverage for dtype coercion, count and offset handling, separators, comments, usecols, missing values, and error surfaces.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-22T08:44:47.279138150Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-24T00:18:01.352340172Z","closed_at":"2026-04-24T00:18:01.349525270Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
